{
  "stem": "9730.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, the Nazis used propaganda as no one else had done until [? them ?]-- then.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I was growing up, you know, radio came into its own.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Hitler knew exactly how to manipulate the masses on the radio.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he knew how his messages-- his vitriolic messages-- would affect them, and, and how he could, you know, pin the blame for everything that was wrong with the economy and with Germany on, on the Jews.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they became-- Jews became the scapegoat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so through radio and through film, the Nazis-- that was a great tool for them to, to get to where they were.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it, it, it was a totally shattering experience for me, to, to find that all these people were turning away from me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what was even worse, that, that some teachers were espousing those, that same ideology.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember a, a gym teacher of ours giving a lecture once in, in class to the effect of-- this is as close to what he said as I can remember.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There are certain elements among us here who are merely guests in this country.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They will be treated OK as long as they behave themselves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But unfortunately, they have not always behaved themselves, and therefore, we cannot guarantee what will happen to them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, this completely undid me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And not, because, perhaps, even of the content, but because I could see that the Nazis were reaching everybody, not only my classmates.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or the, the, the Nazis also had a, sort of a, a way of, of, of doing certain things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "For instance, in the early years, I remember they were marching at, at night sometimes.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
